caption.body: Filmmaker Samuel Abrahams explores the rapidly changing methods of  social interaction as he documents one man’s challenge to find his next  date through face-to-face contact, an increasingly rare approach in the  age of the internet.  See “Offline Dating” by Samuel Abrahams, now playing, in the Video  Arts Gallery, located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2EqhwtJ
